# Invoice QC Service - Project Setup
## Project Structure
```
invoice-qc-service/
├── invoice_qc/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── extractor.py          # PDF extraction logic
│   ├── validator.py          # Validation rules and logic
│   ├── cli.py                # CLI interface
│   ├── schemas.py            # Data models (Pydantic)
│   └── config.py             # Configuration
├── api/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py               # FastAPI application
│   └── routes.py             # API endpoints
├── tests/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── test_extractor.py
│   └── test_validator.py
├── pdfs/                     # Sample invoice PDFs (from provided link)
├── output/                   # Generated outputs
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
├── .env.example
└── .gitignore

```
## Initial Setup Commands

```bash
# Create project directory
mkdir invoice-qc-service
cd invoice-qc-service

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate virtual environment
# On Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate
# On Mac/Linux:
source venv/bin/activate

# Create directory structure
mkdir -p invoice_qc api tests pdfs output

# Create __init__.py files
touch invoice_qc/__init__.py
touch api/__init__.py
touch tests/__init__.py
```

## Dependencies (requirements.txt)

```txt
# Core dependencies
fastapi==0.104.1
uvicorn[standard]==0.24.0
pydantic==2.5.0
python-multipart==0.0.6

# PDF processing
pdfplumber==0.10.3
PyPDF2==3.0.1

# CLI
typer==0.9.0
rich==13.7.0

# Utilities
python-dateutil==2.8.2
regex==2023.10.3

# Testing
pytest==7.4.3
httpx==0.25.2
```

## Quick Install

```bash
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

